The paper is about evaluating image captioning systems, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The method proposed in the paper involves assessing the relevance, extraness, and omission of captions, which requires some level of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG) techniques. The paper also mentions using word embeddings and similarity measures, which are common in information retrieval (cs.IR).
